Silent Aircraft Initiative nke a bụ nnyocha nke Cambridge-MIT Institute mere iji chọpụta ụzọ isi belata mkpọtụ ụgbọ elu nke ukwuu, ruo n'ókè ebe ọ ga-abụ ihe a na-apụghị ịhụ anya nye ndị mmadụ na-anọghị na gburugburu ọdụ  ụgbọ elu.
Emebere ya na Nọvemba 2003, mmemme ahụ nwere nkwado nke Rolls-Royce, Boeing na Marshall Aerospace. Ọ bụ UK Treasury na ndị mmekọ ụlọ ọrụ kwadoro nyocha ahụ
Ihe sonyere Na  ihe ọmụmụ ahụ bụ iji nyochaa ma ọ bụrụ na ịrịda na-aga n'ihu n'ime ọdụ ụgbọ elu ga-ebelata ọkwa mkpọtụ
Nnyocha echiche ga-akwado site na nnwale n'ọhịa site na iji ezigbo ihe akporo jetliners.
Ihe sonyere ma dịkwa zi mkpa nke ọmụmụ ahụ bụ ịmepụta ihe akporo jetliner na injin nke nwere ike izute ebumnuche SAI.
Ntọala a na-ahọrọ bụ ngwakọta nku, na injin dị n'elu nku ahụ, iji chebe ndị na-ekiri ala site na mkpọtụ injin
N'ihi na nku a gwakọtara agwakọta adịghị omimi iji nweta injin abụọ, a tụpụtara nhazi injin anọ.
Ntọala engine kachasị amasị bụ turbofan nwere obere nkwalite, ya bụ oke ikuku ikuku

Nke a na-enye ọsọ ọsọ gas na-adịghị arụ ọrụ nke ọma (ụda ụgbọ elu dị ala) ya mere arụmọrụ dị ala, a pụkwara inweta ya n'oge ọdịda site na iji ebe a na-agbanwe agbanwe na-agbanye ikuku iji weghachite fan
Ọzọkwa, ọgwụgwọ ụda na ntinye na anwụrụ ọkụ nwere ike belata mkpọtụ nke turbomachinery.
